<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Student ID Verification System</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sree+Krushnadevaraya:wght@400;700&display=swap">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="left-section">
      <h1 class="compact-title">Student ID <br> Verification System</h1> <p class="welcome-message">Welcome to the student ID verification system! Accessing this system allows you to verify student IDs <br> swiftly and securely, enhancing overall security.</p>
      <div class="instructions">
        <h3>Here are the steps:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Upload an image file containing the student ID.</li>
          <li>Click the "Verify ID" button.</li>
          <li>The system will display the verification results and student details.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="right-section">
      <h2>Scan an Image File</h2>
      <input type="file" id="student-id-file" accept="image/*">
      <button type="button" id="verify-button">Verify ID</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>


